  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p><em>Effective date: January 1, 2025</em></p>

  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>FreelancePricingCalc ("we," "us," or "our") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and your rights. By using FreelancePricingCalc, you agree to the practices described here.</p>

  <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>We do not collect personally identifiable information. Calculator inputs — your income goals, overhead costs, and billing rates — are processed in your browser and are not transmitted to or stored on our servers. We use Google Analytics 4 to collect anonymous aggregate usage data (pages visited, session duration, general geographic region). This data cannot identify individual users.</p>

  <h2>Cookies</h2>
  <p>We do not use cookies requiring user consent. Google Analytics may set anonymous measurement cookies. We do not use advertising tracking cookies that store personally identifiable information.</p>

  <h2>Advertising</h2>
  <p>This site displays advertisements through Google AdSense. Google may use cookies to serve relevant ads. Opt out at www.google.com/settings/ads.</p>

  <h2>Third-Party Links</h2>
  <p>We may link to IRS publications, BLS resources, and other third-party sites. We are not responsible for their privacy practices.</p>

  <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>This site is not directed at children under 13 and we do not knowingly collect their information.</p>

  <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>Updates are reflected in the effective date. Continued use constitutes acceptance.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>Questions? Contact us at: <strong>hey@theclicklab.agency</strong></p>
